N14: Set Return to Home (RTH) altitude to 100
E15: Flight mode changed to Starting Motors.
E18: Flight mode changed to Manual Takeoff.
N5: Adjust antennas and make sure they are perpendicular to flight direction of aircraft.
E12: Flight mode changed to Auto Landing.
N10: Make sure the area under the aircraft is safe for landing.
N16: Push throttle down to use force landing.
